1. CSS : Cascading Stylesheets 
	- Styling language. (Programming language X)
	- Used for Website layout and design

2. 3 Methods for adding CSS
	- Inline CSS : Directly in html element
	- Internal CSS : Using <style> tags within a single document
	- External CSS : Linking an external .css file (most used)

3. CSS Selectors

a {background-color : yello; }

a : selector
중괄호 : declaration start & end
background-color : property
colon (:) : property/value separator'
yellow : value
semi-colon : declaration separator

4. Diverse colors in CSS

- Just put color names
- Hexadecimal
6 zeros : black
6 f : white
- RGB
rgb(0,0,255) : red, green, blue

5. Font family로 Font를 설정할 수 있음. 

font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
font-size:16px; 
font-weight:normal;

- Simple Setting
font : normal Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; 

6. Box model

margin - border - padding - content
padding : space inside
margin : space outside 

p{
	margin-top:5px
	margin-bottom:5px
	margin-right:5px
	margin-left:5px
}

p{
	margin:5px 10px 5px 10px
}

p{
	margin:5px 10px
}

7. Positioning in CSS

-Static
-Relative
-Absolute
-Fixed
-Initial
-Inherit